\n老將無ring去痴下都話<br />\n自己有隻ring仲走去死敵到痴ring<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83449640fd68b189f5fd29b702b777b2ab032f45","tid":186054,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係二五倫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時變左二五雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果幾年d terms好搞笑<br />\n又退化wade又二五倫</blockquote><br />\n好少可見你唔鳩嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔記得，好似雷定倫都有人叫；<br />\n不過當年退化Wade同三弟啲BigShot仲準過FOJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFoj 對住馬刺game6/7好勁wow <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，我仲記得Game6大三元添；<br />\n但我記得啲關鍵三分唔少都係巴提亞同Miller入既？<br />\n25Ray果球直頭唔使講，<br />\n憎還憎但一定係NBA Final之中其中最重要一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年miller battier ray chalmers好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c49732d757c621415cf41867a8a6714b88d910f","tid":186054,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ray gun轉個陣都唔算當打<br />\n但KD條撚屌仲係當打就走撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKD果年比人打完轉隊真心仆街；<br />\n不過我投比二五倫係因為明明係綠軍Cham到，<br />\n點解要轉投熱水反打綠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然背後有同RR9既不和等等，<br />\n早排都見到有報導係講緊08當年Cham之後慶功唔預Ray，<br />\n係因為綠軍班人都睇唔起Ray當年轉隊入綠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都係果句未知今年邊個Cham，<br />\n但當年二五雷加埋熱水巨頭既化學反應簡直係全聯盟最被人鬧既球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實綠軍打多年都唔似會champ到<br />\n三老頭又老一年<br />\n熱火三巨頭如日中天</blockquote><br />\n2012都7場僅敗比熱火<br />\n2013有咩可能贏到"},{"pid":"87e97ac70dab6ac498835fccfcad5e77a60cd90a","tid":186054,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二五倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老將無ring去痴下都話<br />\n自己有隻ring仲走去死敵到痴ring<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢入唔到個球3分應該會無咁多人憎<br />\n唔係痴既 但幫左個串皇奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1af73af493cd72eee4a6a5c8e8bffb9d3b74bc","tid":186054,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>kd狗十萬倍<br />\nray gun已經過曬當打時間<br />\n綠軍仲要唔專重佢<br />\n去痴多隻ring都無可厚非<br />\n但kd以上都無出現過就去痴ring<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果kd同wb本身反哂面先走就唔會屌佢咁多<br />\n但係睇wb反應好明顯係賤種kd 25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49456cbf0053f766a56a6dff55fdf15721c9ed2","tid":186054,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T06:37:21.000Z","msg":"講25梗係皮鞋道理"},{"pid":"6d12188aa496ac45a8660511762963afba270a25","tid":186054,"uid":9098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd531546d5ce18089d8b61b988a710dc4a57be2","tid":186054,"uid":90630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T03:33:48.000Z","msg":"ray gun都叫25 自己無喇喇比人踢走 咁咪揀隊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去熱火又可以爭冠 又可以證明自己重有貨<br />\n問題何在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己唔要人 人地贏咗 輸打贏要就話人地25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d3e8dd2ef7a992571428383d7da72935dd14bd","tid":186054,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT